# Constitution — {{project_name}}

The non-negotiable invariants of this project. An agent must re-validate
against these at plan time, implement time, and review time. Violating an
invariant is a stop condition, not a judgment call.

Curated by `/vibe-constitution` on {{retrofitted_at}}. Amend deliberately
(an invariant change is a real decision — record why in the relevant
handoff or CHANGELOG).

> **How this differs from CLAUDE.md:** CLAUDE.md tells you *how to work here*
> (commands, conventions, session ritual). This file tells you *what this
> project will not violate*. CLAUDE.md is guidance; the constitution is law.

